@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@orgId = xw
@sessionToken =

### Test GET /api/v1/billing/subscription (COM COOKIE)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/billing/subscription
X-Organization-Id: {{orgId}}
Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{sessionToken}}

### Test GET /api/v1/billing/subscription (COM SECURE COOKIE)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/billing/subscription
X-Organization-Id: {{orgId}}
Cookie: __Secure-better-auth.session_token={{sessionToken}}

### Test GET /api/v1/organizations (Para verificar se auth funciona)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/organizations
Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{sessionToken}}